{"tid":422570,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個老母煮野食嘅on9野","createTime":"2017-10-03T07:14:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-03T09:09:07.000Z","uid":41619,"like":3,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"1fd323a77551edb924acd326c3dbeedf63312d11","tid":422570,"uid":41619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T07:14:35.000Z","msg":"屌<br />\n次次煮公仔麵唔會落湯<br />\n用水煮完就咁放落碗<br />\n即煮即食勉強都冇問題<br />\n一擺耐咗<br />\n又淋又乾<br />\n一夾就爛<br />\n慘過食糊仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n次次講完都唔聽<br />\n真係好撚火滾<br />\n<br />\nP.S. 唔該唔好話咩 「老母唔煮 你冇得食」"},{"pid":"7413c2230278b13dbf4b991237cad06c7589025b","tid":422570,"uid":134683,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T07:15:32.000Z","msg":"老母煮乜我都會食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a72638c39251e968a4bdc0cca4a259a8327f709","tid":422570,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T07:16:17.000Z","msg":"冇<br />\n<br />\n冇乜自創on9菜式<br />\n<br />\n煮都係普通家常便飯<br />\n<br />\n多謝媽媽"},{"pid":"d3a5f1cbf6536a9a446d38f06e6b2a07ab9b050c","tid":422570,"uid":41619,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T07:18:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老母煮乜我都會食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n次次煮到咁<br />\n唔食又晒<br />\n食嘅話佢又唔覺得有問題"},{"pid":"e616cf7bd1300a5a7382d09dcbc13ea0d36c7d6a","tid":422570,"uid":28624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T07:19:28.000Z","msg":"唔知點解老母每次煮親麵類<br />\n都會煮到d麵斷哂爛哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n究竟係點做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a56833200ccfb35f1b96dc8b3648702b2b35a13c","tid":422570,"uid":41619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T07:19:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇<br />\n<br />\n冇乜自創on9菜式<br />\n<br />\n煮都係普通家常便飯<br />\n<br />\n多謝媽媽</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我番工帶飯<br />\n我呀媽煮啲野食又好正常<br />\n唯獨係煮個公仔麵都可以咁on9"},{"pid":"0513dfaca24e583fd8a22bd9de12fc01af3c4ace","tid":422570,"uid":41619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T07:20:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔知點解老母每次煮親麵類<br />\n都會煮到d麵斷哂爛哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n究竟係點做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一係佢煮得太淋<br />\n我自己煮的話<br />\n會特登早少少熄火<br />\n等佢唔好淋 咁就有咁易爛<br />\n仲彈牙啲"},{"pid":"2abd41896ebdf012a916020661beacac0328b4a3","tid":422570,"uid":149499,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T07:40:06.000Z","msg":"食剩m記薯條唔掉，第2日有薯條蒸水蛋食，夠唔夠on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a95e9314ad93e5e14ea6ddb8f8823a1be9e2c107","tid":422570,"uid":54451,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T07:42:20.000Z","msg":"冇老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"119ea3ca7dcf7510ac2777237e4501629cd8662d","tid":422570,"uid":13555,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T07:44:38.000Z","msg":"咁咪自己煮囉<br />\n又要人煮又咁多意見"},{"pid":"ead454d44d9d4f0711fc1436cfdbf8fb14aece88","tid":422570,"uid":83646,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T07:45:59.000Z","msg":"煮餸淨左d芥末汁 佢另一日攞左撈白飯 話人地葡汁飯都係禁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d38f3dca20f8b454b2167bf48320bf71f5f309c8","tid":422570,"uid":5159,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T07:49:08.000Z","msg":"煲湯有魚骨<br />\n番茄蛋有魚骨<br />\n炒菜心有魚骨<br />\n皮蛋瘦有魚骨<br />\n<img